d avenge his family. With the help of Fu Xi, the high priest of the Shenyin Ministry, Prince Wu Geng sought out allies for his quest to take down the Yun Clan and win back his freedom.</p>","tmdb_id":231040,"cast":["Nhậm Gia Luân","Hình Phi","Chúc Tự Đan","Nghiêm Ngật Khoan","Chu Chính Đình","Mễ Nhiệt"],"director":["Chongchong Liu"],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"231040","season":1,"vote_average":7.5,"vote_count":6},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Nhậm Gia Luân","name_vi":"Nhậm Gia Luân","name_original":"Ren Jialun","tmdb_id":2084465,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5sBfnbHbTmNriFPGGD12mPpTNNO.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2084465"},{"name":"Hình Phi","name_vi":"Hình Phi","name_original":"Xing Fei","tmdb_id":1737082,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pQaUc5pJRaGwD8iwwzY1Z2YbrEj.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1737082"},{"name":"Chúc Tự Đan","name_vi":"Chúc Tự Đan","name_original":"Zhu Xudan","tmdb_id":1838200,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bfqvBRuDi56O2WB1Hvg6IPeITlm.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1838200"},{"name":"Nghiêm Ngật Khoan","name_vi":"Nghiêm Ngật Khoan","name_original":"Kevin Yan","tmdb_id":1407599,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oCUiTeAnwmjc0tof4SFziOExIK7.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1407599"},{"name":"Chu Chính Đình","name_vi":"Chu Chính Đình","name_original":"Zhu Zhengting","tmdb_id":2435309,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ovZZOqe9MaojSoT9h0aHPPJJYYi.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2435309"},{"name":"Mễ Nhiệt","name_vi":"Mễ Nhiệt","name_original":"Merxat","tmdb_id":1982964,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/y7lTmzX6rWBlMBfF6zep0FFDV9Y.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1982964"}],"tmdb_checked":true,"pubjs_url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/gotvtop102/pjs102@main/pubjs/li/liet-diem.json"}